Message.SourceString: The door refuses to open. Powerful necromantic seals bar your entry. You will need the full power of Imaru's curse to break through them.
Message.LocalizedString: The door refuses to open. Powerful necromantic seals bar your entry. You will need the full power of Imaru's curse to break through them.

Message.SourceString: If you bring me her head, then I'll turn it into something useful. Grim, yes, but one must have something to put in the filing cabinet.
Message.LocalizedString: If you bring me her head, then I'll turn it into something useful. Grim, yes, but one must have something to put in the filing cabinet.

Message.SourceString: Unleash the curse, destroying the fragments, and face Imaru?
Message.LocalizedString: Unleash the curse, destroying the fragments, and face Imaru?

Message.SourceString: When she's slain, bring me her head. Gruesome, I know, but I will need it to give her spirit peace at least. Also it helps with the paperwork.
Message.LocalizedString: When she's slain, bring me her head. Gruesome, I know, but I will need it to give her spirit peace at least. Also it helps with the paperwork.

Message.SourceString: Here let me take that dragon head from you.
Message.LocalizedString: Here let me take that dragon head from you.

Message.SourceString: Now that you're borrowing the power of her curse, Imaru is finally vulnerable. She's had centuries of souls to feast on, and she's still one of Kuldra's draconic generals, so she won't go down easily. Make sure you're prepared.
Message.LocalizedString: Now that you're borrowing the power of her curse, Imaru is finally vulnerable. She's had centuries of souls to feast on, and she's still one of Kuldra's draconic generals, so she won't go down easily. Make sure you're prepared.

Message.SourceString: Imaru the devourer is dead. Good! She was a potential problem that I did not want to have to deal with. You've done well, adventurer, better than the last few I sent anyway.
Message.LocalizedString: Imaru the devourer is dead. Good! She was a potential problem that I did not want to have to deal with. You've done well, adventurer, better than the last few I sent anyway.

Message.SourceString: I knew one of you would luck out eventually, I'm glad it was you. Oh, yes, sorry, no chosen ones here. But ignore that, you did good, better than the rest, so you deserve what you came for.
Message.LocalizedString: I knew one of you would luck out eventually, I'm glad it was you. Oh, yes, sorry, no chosen ones here. But ignore that, you did good, better than the rest, so you deserve what you came for.

Message.SourceString: Hrmm, you appear to be a little overburdened. Shed yourself some of thy worldly trappings and then come speak to me again.
Message.LocalizedString: Hrmm, you appear to be a little overburdened. Shed yourself some of thy worldly trappings and then come speak to me again.

Message.SourceString: A foul thing, really. Corrupted beyond repair. I almost pity her. Still, you're not interested in that, I feel you'll enjoy this much more.
Message.LocalizedString: A foul thing, really. Corrupted beyond repair. I almost pity her. Still, you're not interested in that, I feel you'll enjoy this much more.

Message.SourceString: Now, I have an enormously unpleasant cleanup to do. So you'll forgive me if I get back to work.
Message.LocalizedString: Now, I have an enormously unpleasant cleanup to do. So you'll forgive me if I get back to work.
